Police looking for ‘AC bike-borne stashers’ (Mechanic helps cops nab bike ‘challan-hogger’)

New Delhi: Out to catch Mirza Ghalib challan-hogger bikers, a police team nabbed a 40-year-old mechanic here yesterday, Manoj, alias Bunty, who they had no option, but to let go citing ‘lack of evidence.’ The Delhi Police has been crusading against two-wheelers violating traffic rules since in 2004.
